<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idefc207da-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s4905"><num value="4905">§ 4905.</num><heading> Regulations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary may issue such regulations as may be necessary to carry out the provisions of this chapter and the powers vested in the Secretary under this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idefc207db-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/99/198/tXVI/s1646">Pub. L. 99–198, title XVI, § 1646</ref>, <date date="1985-12-23">Dec. 23, 1985</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/99/1624">99 Stat. 1624</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
